Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这一章节的《Wolfram 笔记本介绍》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讲解了一个更合适的表格格式化工具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这里所示的表格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and is specifically about options for setting up details,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,例如分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有交错底色的横行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有调整表格中每个单元格外观的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们从第一个样例开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是生成一个表格范例的输入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,执行这个输入，我们得到了一个输出单元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我将把它转换为文本单元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大多数单元格内都是纯文本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个输入使用了 Grid 内置符号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grid 内置符号的第一个参数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是真正被放在表格中的数组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,该数组给出了表头和占位符
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有六个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“背景”(Background) 选项设置表格的背景为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,横行交错使用白色和灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我点击表格内部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后按下 Ctrl + 回车 以增加更多的行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,交错的背景颜色会在新行中继续延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“排列” (Alignment) 选项指定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每一列中文本的水平对齐方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和每一行中文本的垂直对齐方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,“分割线” (Dividers) 选项用来绘制行与行之间的分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是定义表头之下绘制粗分割线的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,below the heading is specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“基本样式” (BaseStyle) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,定义了表格中文字所用的字体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最后，对象大小 (ItemSize) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,定义了每一列允许占用的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“间隔” (Spacings) 选项定义了列于列之间的空隙大小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即使被这些选项控制的细节非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它的基本思想依然很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以发现，许多选项都有着相似的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只需观察他们的效果即可阐明表格中的这些设计\N （译注：需要一定的英语基础）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,on a generic table.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一个带有占位符文本的表格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它的“边框” (Frame) 选项被设置为“全部” (All)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以帮助我们清楚的观察行和列
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,从“背景” (Background) 选项开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以设置成单个颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以改变整个网格的背景颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but the general form of the Background option
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个带有三个参数的列表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其中第一个参数定义了每一列的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个参数定义了每一行的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第三个参数可以用来定义表格中特定单元格的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,举个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在第一个参数中输入红色 (Red) ，绿色 (Green) 和蓝色 (Blue)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,会使前三列变成红色、绿色和蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以列表形式给出颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会让颜色在表格中重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,例如  这样会使第一列变为红色\N译注：“这样”指下一台词时屏幕所示代码
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后剩下的列被交替重复的绿色和蓝色所填充
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,行也采用同样的参数结构
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,例如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们在“背景” (Background) 选项中第二个参数处定义相同的颜色序列 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就会得到第一行是红色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的行是交错的绿色和蓝色的表格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,“背景” (Background) 选项的第三个参数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能用于具体定义特定单元格的背景颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,例如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以指定第四行第七列的单元格采用橙色背景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“分割线” (Dividers) 选项的原理与之相仿 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,相似的还有排列 (Alignment) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,乃至所有控制行和列的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,例如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里给出了能使表格每隔三列有一道竖分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,并在第二行之上有一道横分割线的“分割线” (Dividers) 选项的参数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如同“背景” (Background) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“分割线” (Dividers) 选项的参数也是一个列表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,列表中第一个参数定义了竖分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个参数定义了横分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,分割线也有自己的样式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,例如
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会使竖分割线以粗线和灰色细线交替出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,并且使表头下方的横分割线显示为红色粗线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,带着我们学到的普适道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们回到开始的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我将继续操作并向表格中填写一些内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“背景” (Background) 选项的参数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,指定每一行交错使用白色和灰色背景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“排列” (Alignment) 选项指定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,第一列中的元素应当水平居中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,第二行则是右对齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像平时数字的对齐方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,第三列的元素采用左对齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“分割线” (Dividers) 选项的参数定义了表头之下的粗分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,浅灰色的分割线与每一行的背景色合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,除了最后一行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里分割线显示了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就像表格末尾的浅灰色直线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“预设格式” (BaseStyle) 选项定义了用于表格中所有元素的默认字体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“项大小” (ItemSize) 参数定义了每一列的宽度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,specifies the width of each column.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The first two columns are given as scaled amounts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which means that they are scaled to a fraction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the formatting width,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is related to the width of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以列宽会随着窗口宽度而更改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with the width of the display,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在表格可能会在不同窗口下展示时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种比较理想的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最后  “间隔” (Spacings) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在最后两列间添加了一些空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一种学习这些选项做了什么的好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是尝试这些选项的不同参数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后观察表格的显示效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,例如  这里有一个简单的可交互 (Manipulate) 程序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它会提供一个用于调整列与列之间空隙的控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for adjusting the space between the last two columns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,与调整 Grid 内置符号的选项不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a separate strategy for specifying styles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is to use Item expressions as elements in the table
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and to specify options within each Item expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,例如  相比于使用“背景” (Background) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来定义特定单元格的背景色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of a particular entry in the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个能达到相同效果的方法是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是使用 Item 内置符号作用于对应的元素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,并且在 Item 函数体内包含“背景” (Background) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in that Item expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一个与此相关的特性是使用特殊内置符号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,SpanFromLeft. SpanFromAbove, SpanFromBoth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来让表格中的项占用不止一行或一列
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or more than one column.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,例如  这里有一个被占位符填充的小表格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用内置符号 SpanFromLeft 替换其中一个占位符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with the special symbol SpanFromLeft
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,会使这个单元格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和左侧的单元格合并
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,内置符号 SpanFromAbove
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和 SpanFromBoth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能用于向上合并单元格和双向合并单元格\N译注：双向指向左和向上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 如下操作最终可以达到相同的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,选中想要合并的项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and choosing Make Spanning from the Table/Matrix submenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,使用数次上述工具后  我们的到了最终的样例
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们刚才所展示的两个表格中的第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that were shown earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,及生成它所需的输入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这一输入仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,采用了带有几个参数的 Grid 内置符号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“项大小”  (ItemSize) 选项定义列的宽度为 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with a width of three,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(?) 这意味着 3 将个单位叫做 em
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An em is a unit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等于当前字体的磅数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果省略了项大小 (ItemSize) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那么列宽会调整为与最宽的项相同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the column,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which here gives a table with columns
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它似乎太窄了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 ItemSize 选项被添加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来使表格不那么狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“边框” (Frame) 选项绘制分割线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和表格周围的边框
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“排列” (Alignment) 选项的参数定义了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个元素（项）水平、竖直均居中对齐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“背景” (Background) 选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,定义了表头为淡灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下部分交错出现橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和天蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个表格使用背景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,作为元素“真” (T) 和“假” (F) 的颜色信号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Background option happens in this example
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to give the correct color for all of the entries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,except for one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where the background is specified in an Item expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that Item expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the color for that item would be light blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which doesn't follow the intended color code.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This table also includes two SpanFromAbove entries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which are there to generate the two items in the first column
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that span more than one row.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the examples for this section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A good source for additional information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the documentation for the Grid function
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and related functions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially this tutorial on grids, rows and columns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is of course almost always useful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to just construct a generic table
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and try these things out for yourself.
